claim.claim-text:
A tower pantry (50) in a refrigerator (100), comprising:
a guide mechanism (51) mounted on a bottom (10c) of an opened space inside a refrigerating room (10);
a basket (53) attached to the guide mechanism (51) and configured to move forward and backward on the guide mechanism (51);
frames (54) that are fastened to corners of the basket (53) and that extend vertically from the basket (53), the frames (54) having a length that is greater than a height of a gallon size beverage container; and
a frame cover (56) fastened on the frames (54) and defining a space that accommodates the gallon size beverage container in the basket (53).
